snippet: If the winds cooperate, Felix Baumgartner will try again to make the highest jump in history and become the first sky diver to break the sound barrier.
abstract: Daredevil Felix Baumgartner plans to attempt to make highest jump in history and become first sky diver to break sound barrier; will use helium balloon to reach an altitude of 120,000 feet in the stratosphere; earlier attempt was canceled due to weather.
lead_paragraph: If the winds cooperate, Felix Baumgartner will try again to make the highest jump in history and become the first sky diver to break the sound barrier.

headline.main: New Mexico: Another Try for Record-Seeking Jumper
